author: trobits
body: Go to [trobits.com](http://trobits.com), signup, and visit often. We need traffic to generate revenue from ads; then use the revenue to burn SHIB. With significant burns, we should see price go up

author: trobits
body: By burning, the coins are sent to a wallet and can NEVER be used again. The coins are gone FOREVER. The burn wallet is provided on Trobits as well as the transaction reference for each burn. That way, anyone can verify that the coins were indeed burned!
